sequenceDiagram
  actor Analyst
  participant Web as React App
  participant Cognito as Cognito
  participant API as CreditFlow.Api
  participant DDB as DynamoDB
  participant SNS as SNS Domain Topic
  participant SQS as Decision Queue
  participant Worker as Decision Worker

  Analyst->>Web: Fill and submit loan application
  Web->>Cognito: Use authenticated session
  Web->>API: POST /applications
  API->>API: Validate request and idempotency key
  API->>DDB: Store application as Submitted
  API->>DDB: Store timeline event
  API->>SNS: Publish LoanApplicationSubmitted
  SNS->>SQS: Deliver event to Decision Queue
  API-->>Web: 202 Accepted with applicationId
  Web-->>Analyst: Show submitted status

  SQS->>Worker: Invoke worker with queued message
  Worker->>DDB: Mark application as Processing
  Worker->>Worker: Run deterministic decision rules
  Worker->>DDB: Store decision and update final status
  Worker->>DDB: Store timeline event
  Worker->>SNS: Publish LoanDecisionCompleted
